Titolo: In Verbis Virtus

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: In Verbis Virtus is a downloadable adventure video game developed by the Italian video game developer Indomitus Games. It is early access for release on May 22, 2014 for Microsoft Windows. In Verbis Virtus is a first-person game where the player uses a microphone to cast spells by actually reciting the incantation. It mixes action and puzzle elements in a fantasy setting.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
